Class FitsOutput

java.lang.Object
  edu.harvard.hul.ois.fits.FitsOutput

public class FitsOutput
extends java.lang.Object

This class acts as a wrapper aroudn the fitsXML JDOM Document and provides convenience methods for converting the FITS XML format to standard technical metdata schemas, accessing identification, file info, and metadata elements
